@node history

History

1.2 (28.5.98)

- MUI Interface
- Commodity support
- 3 different qualifier as hotkey
- Prefs saved in Tooltypes (reg)
- Hotkeyprefs
- Switch how hotkey work
- Installer
- AmigaGuide Docs

1.1 (27.5.98)

- completely rewritten in AmigaE (bug fixes and safer)
- can now be started from wb
- included lowlevel.library in archive

1.0 (20.5.98)

- first release

@endnode

@node future

Future

- "parent"-button to reopen parent window
- "parent&close"-button to reopen parent window and close the old one.
- Keyfile-System (RSA)
- WB-Window Manager
- ScalOS usage
- Locale usage in the prefs
- docs,lacales and installer in spanish and italy

@endnode
